        <h1>Dan Matthew</h1>
        <span class="subtitle">Interaction Designer</span>
      </hgroup>
      <p class="abstract">
        Experienced interaction designer with a commitment to creating inclusive
        and user-centred digital products. Strong expertise in accessibility standards. Offers a proven track record of identifying and resolving complex design problems.
      </p>
